thread.title: Saturday's college scores

author: sun-sentinel.com
title: Saturday's college scores
text:
A look at the college football scores from Saturday, Oct. 17:
How the Top 25 fared
No. 1 Ohio State (6-0) beat Penn State 38-10. Next: at Rutgers, Saturday.
No. 2 Baylor (6-0) beat West Virginia 62-38. Next: vs. Iowa State, Saturday.
No. 3 TCU (7-0) beat Iowa State 45-21. Next: vs. West Virginia, Oct. 29.
No. 4 Utah (6-0) beat Arizona State 34-18. Next: at Southern Cal, Saturday.
No. 5 Clemson (6-0) beat Boston College 34-17. Next: at Miami, Saturday.
No. 6 LSU (6-0) beat No. 8 Florida 35-28. Next: vs. Western Kentucky, Saturday.
No. 7 Michigan State (7-0) beat No. 12 Michigan 27-23. Next: vs. Indiana, Saturday.
No. 8 Florida (6-1) lost to No. 6 LSU 35-28. Next: vs. Georgia at Jacksonville, Fla., Oct. 31.
No. 9 Texas A&M (5-1) lost to No. 10 Alabama 41-23. Next: at No. 13 Mississippi, Saturday.
No. 10 Alabama (6-1) beat No. 9 Texas A&M 41-23. Next: vs. Tennessee, Saturday.
No. 11 Florida State (6-0) beat Louisville 41-21. Next: at Georgia Tech, Saturday.
No. 12 Michigan (5-2) lost to No. 7 Michigan State 27-23. Next: at Minnesota, Oct. 31.
No. 13 Mississippi (5-2) lost to Memphis 37-24. Next: vs. No. 9 Texas A&M, Saturday.
No. 14 Notre Dame (6-1) beat Southern Cal 41-31. Next: at Temple, Oct. 31.
No. 15 Stanford (5-1) beat No. 18 UCLA 56-35, Thursday. Next: vs. Washington, Saturday, Oct 24.
No. 16 Oklahoma State (6-0) did not play. Next: vs. Kansas, Saturday.
No. 17 Iowa (7-0) beat No. 20 Northwestern 40-10. Next: vs. Maryland, Oct. 31.
No. 18 UCLA (4-2) lost to No. 15 Stanford 56-35, Thursday. Next: vs. No. 23 California, Thursday Oct 22.
No. 19 Oklahoma (5-1) beat Kansas State 55-0. Next: vs. Texas Tech, Saturday.
No. 20 Northwestern (5-2) lost to No. 17 Iowa 40-10. Next: at Nebraska, Saturday.
No. 21 Boise St. (5-2) lost to Utah State 52-26, Friday. Next: vs. Wyoming, Saturday.
No. 22 Toledo (6-0) beat Eastern Michigan 63-20. Next: at UMass, Saturday.
No. 23 California (5-1) did not play. Next: at No. 18 UCLA, Thursday, Oct. 22.
No. 24 Houston (6-0) beat Tulane 42-7, Friday. Next: at UCF, Saturday.
No. 25 Duke (5-1) did not play. Next: at Virginia Tech, Saturday.
